title: Dev Fund Future Marketing Opinion Poll
body:
YMEN and MUTANT are great products. we can get them to more people.
achieving critical mass on price/supply will require more people to be on board.

how much do you think should be allocated for competitions and marketing to design and distribute official ads and merchandise?

================================================
[4] 10% of new MUTANT tokens routed to Dev Fund marketing campaign.

[1] 5% of new MUTANT tokens routed to Dev Fund marketing campaign.

[2] 2% of new MUTANT tokens routed to Dev Fund marketing campaign.

[3] No Dev fund marketing.
================================================

this is a community opinion poll, for consideration of future elected/appointed council. voting will not affect the changes discussed.
author: 0x225D29eb77a18a7E520c9bB431c5bd8B1bE376A5
